             <div class="PropTable11 ViewPropertyPageFonts" style="color: #1D2D33;">
              Bucks at Lady Barron is situated in the heart of popular Lady Barron on Flinders Island. It is located next door to Flinders Island Lodge in Franklin Parade where you can stroll in for a quiet drink, or an a la carte meal if you dont feel like cooking.
              <br/>
              Your stepping off point to explore the history and beauty of the Furneaux Islands. A modern comfortable home boosting beautiful views of Franklin Sound and surrounding islands.
